      "text": [
        " الرَّجُلِ وَ الْمَرْأَةِ يُوجَدَانِ فِي لِحَافٍ وَاحِدٍ قَالَ يُجْلَدَانِ مِائَةً مِائَةً غَيْرَ سَوْطٍ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from Muhammad Bin Isa, from Yunus, from Mufazzal Bin Salih, from Zayd Al Shahaam, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> regarding the man and the woman both found to be in one quilt. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘They would both be whipped one hundred one lashes each, apart from one lash’."
        ]
